trans-unit.source: Debug Hadoop in HDInsight: Error messages | Microsoft Azure

trans-unit.source: Learn about the error messages you might receive when administering HDInsight using PowerShell, and steps you can take to recover.
trans-unit.target: Learn about the error messages you might receive when administering HDInsight using PowerShell, and steps you can take to recover.

trans-unit.source: Debug Hadoop in HDInsight: Interpret error messages
trans-unit.target: Debug Hadoop in HDInsight: Interpret error messages

trans-unit.source: The error messages itemized in this topic are provided to help the users of Hadoop in Azure HDInsight understand possible error conditions that they can encounter when administering the service using Azure PowerShell and to advise them on the steps which can be taken to recover from the error.
trans-unit.target: The error messages itemized in this topic are provided to help the users of Hadoop in Azure HDInsight understand possible error conditions that they can encounter when administering the service using Azure PowerShell and to advise them on the steps which can be taken to recover from the error.

trans-unit.source: Some of these error messages could also be seen in the Azure preview portal when it is used to manage HDInsight clusters.
trans-unit.target: Some of these error messages could also be seen in the Azure preview portal when it is used to manage HDInsight clusters.

trans-unit.source: But other error messages you might encounter there are less granular due to the constraints on the remedial actions possible in this context.
trans-unit.target: But other error messages you might encounter there are less granular due to the constraints on the remedial actions possible in this context.

trans-unit.source: Other error messages are provided in the contexts where the mitigation is obvious.
trans-unit.target: Other error messages are provided in the contexts where the mitigation is obvious.

trans-unit.source: If the constraints on parameters are violated, for example, the message pops-up in on the right side of the box where the value was entered.
trans-unit.target: If the constraints on parameters are violated, for example, the message pops-up in on the right side of the box where the value was entered.
